about:
Crossover is the world's #1 source of full-time remote jobs. Our clients offer top-tier pay for top-tier talent. We're recruiting this role for our client, Trilogy. Have you got what it takes?

Have you read the key texts in motivational psychology and gamification, wondering how this knowledge can change the future of education? Trilogy is dedicated to maximizing learning outcomes across its diverse EdTech portfolio, and we're searching for a strategist who can combine the science of engagement with a passion for AI.
jobDescription:
- Update and maintain the overall health of the company main websites and the corporate blog; work on their design system and consistency

- Create attractive landing pages to promote the company products and services

- Focus on improving the overall user experience and conversion rates

- Cooperate with copywriters, web developers, advertising specialists; gather feedback from users and stakeholders and use it to make improvements on the website

- Be the main contact point for all design-related topics on the corporate website

- Improve existing design solutions while also continuing to evolve the brand language.
qualifications:
- Strong knowledge of Figma, Adobe products

- Strong typography and composition skills

- Knowledge of how to create and work with design systems, UI kits

- Neatness, pixel perfect approach to accuracy, striving for file hygiene

- Well-prepared specifications for the devteam and diligent asset handoff

- Portfolio showcasing a clear understanding of simplicity, typography, and interactions

- Readiness to spend enough time to get to know the companyâ€™s fintech products, no fear of complex fintech topics

- Deadline consciousness

- General understanding of Web technologies (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)

- B2+/C1 English

- Open-mindedness and team-first attitude, being able to criticize in a friendly manner and accept constructive criticism

- Willingness to grow personally and professionally as a web designer

- An empathic and patient professional
